The help screens follow the same pattern as the program.  Whenever the help key
is pressed, this help screen will be displayed.  To recieve help on a
particular subject, follow the path which was taken when running the program
until coming to the screen of your choice.

In help, F8 will return to the previous menu, F9 is used for more help, and F10
exits from help.



To obtain help for any of the following subjects, press the function key next
to the desired choice.

        F1  Main Menu
        F2  Main Screen
        F3  Chart Characteristics (First insert Specific Help diskette if not
            using hard disk)




        F10 Exit from Help

Press F10 to leave the help mode
